 on the lips, but it’s also possible it was used in other ways. A lipstick-blush combination kit? An ancient girl had options.</p><br><h2 class=\"subheader inline-placeholder\" data-editable=\"text\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/subheader/instances/cm4j0q565000s3b6q9j63r00h@published\" data-component-name=\"subheader\" id=\"history-making-cave-art\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-subheader__font-family); clear: inherit; padding: 16px 0px 8px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: var(--theme-subheader-h2__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-subheader-h2__line-height); max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.297px;\"><b>History-making cave art</b></h2><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4j0emgh00103b6q47qp2q2k@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.297px;\">Nearly 700 miles southwest of Buenos Aires, archaeologists from Argentina and Chile discovered the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2024/03/08/style/argentina-patagonia-cave-paintings-earliest-scn/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">earliest known cave paintings</a>&nbsp;in South America. Dating back 8,200 years, the 895 works of art come from the Huenul 1 cave, a mammoth rock shelter of around 6,700 square feet.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4j0emgh000e3b6q87z0oyvo@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\"></p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/image/instances/cm4j19nbm002n3b6q0kz9nfyp@published\" class=\"image_large image_large__hide-placeholder image_large--eq-extra-small image_large--eq-small\" data-image-variation=\"image_large\" data-name=\"2024-03-07T110147Z_1141475861_RC2FE6A6SBX8_RTRMADP_3_ARGENTINA-ARCHAEOLOGY.jpg\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image_large--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image_large--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-original-height=\"1125\" data-original-width=\"2000\" data-url=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/2024-03-07t110147z-1141475861-rc2fe6a6sbx8-rtrmadp-3-argentina-archaeology.jpg?c=original\" data-editable