tyle=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">esports</a>&nbsp;and Formula One in recent years</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000j3b6m4tx334cp@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000j3b6m4tx334cp@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dj9r2qksh/image/upload/v1734784459/newspaper_images/igb8ktt5scinx9aboueq.png\" style=\"width: 100%;\">.<span style=\"color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">The nation claims the investment is part of Saudi Vision 2030, a project driven by Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman to diversify the economy and situate Saudi Arabia as one of the world’s leading countries.</span></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000l3b6matsmd4v5@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Its focus on soccer, perhaps the world’s most popular sport, has been particularly notable.<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2023/09/20/sport/saudi-arabia-soccer-spl-bin-salman-intl-spt-cmd-dg/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\"></a></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000m3b6m5edvwxaj@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">In recent years, Saudi Arabia has purchased a storied soccer club – English Premier League team&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2021/11/09/football/newcastle-united-fans-against-saudi-ownership-spt-intl-cmd/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Newcastle United</a>&nbsp;– and convinced a host of legends to join the Saudi Pro League – most notably Cristiano Ronaldo, Karim Benzema and Neymar Jr.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000n3b6m37upyza7@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">In the process, the Saudi crown prince, widely known by his initials MBS, has struck up a public friendship with FIFA President Gianni Infantino, who has continued to welcome investment from the Gulf nation in the sport.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000o3b6mfk7pqftd@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Hosting a World Cup, then, is the cherry on the top – the pièce de résistance of the Kingdom’s foray into the sport.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000p3b6m57vaxj8w@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Unsurprisingly, the country has big plans for the tournament. It has committed to significant infrastructure projects, in addition to building or renovating 11 stadiums and 185,000 new hotel rooms.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000q3b6mk35o453n@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">But, according to human rights groups, the Saudi World Cup in 2034 will come at a cost.</p><h2 class=\"subheader inline-placeholder\" data-editable=\"text\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/subheader/instances/cm4ir4vbh002r3b6muv68owkz@published\" data-component-name=\"subheader\" id=\"human-rights-concerns\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; clear: inherit; padding: 16px 0px 8px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: var(--theme-subheader-h2__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-subheader-h2__line-height); max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><b>Human rights concerns</b></h2><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000s3b6mdq2ytbrs@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">A recent&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.hrw.org/report/2024/12/04/die-first-and-ill-pay-you-later/saudi-arabias-giga-projects-built-widespread\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">report</a>&nbsp;from HRW, titled “Die First, and I’ll Pay You Later,” argues that Saudi Arabia is using the tournament to “wash away its poor human rights reputation.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000t3b6miz7n7e56@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">The report primarily focuses on the treatment of migrant workers, who HRW says will bear the brunt of building Saudi’s World Cup dream.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000t3b6miz7n7e56@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000u3b6mvx2pr2ig@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Many migrant workers still exist in the “Kafala” sponsorship system, which ties people to a specific employer. HRW said in a June statement that employees are “vulnerable to widespread abuse, including contract substitution, exorbitant recruitment fees, non-payment of wages, confiscation of passports by employers, and forced labor.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000u3b6mvx2pr2ig@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000v3b6mnc6pozku@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Despite a series of reforms announced by Saudi Arabia in recent years, employers “still hold disproportionate control over workers,” HRW said.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000x3b6m403qzjyk@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">There are also concerns about press freedom, the treatment of LGTBQ+ groups and the rights of women, among others.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000y3b6mgo0enpaa@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">In a recent report published by FIFA which evaluated Saudi’s bid, the human rights risk was categorized as “<a href=\"https://digitalhub.fifa.com/m/51d8a13714827f1d/original/FIFA-World-Cup-2034-Bid-Evaluation-Report.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">medium</a>.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000y3b6mgo0enpaa@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000z3b6mq9t1efar@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">The report and designation are based on information provided by AS&amp;H Clifford Chance, a law firm based in Riyadh which was tasked with providing an independent human rights assessment.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk000z3b6mq9t1efar@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00103b6mm5thgh7y@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">In its report, FIFA added that “there is a good potential that hosting the competition could help contribute to positive human rights impacts in the context of Saudi Arabia’s Vision 2030.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00113b6mo9vph710@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">It also noted “considerable work and level of concrete commitment demonstrated by the bid and its key stakeholders, together with the demonstrable rate of progress and the 10-year time horizon are mitigating factors to consider.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00113b6mo9vph710@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00113b6mo9vph710@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dj9r2qksh/image/upload/v1734784461/newspaper_images/meubl8st7ldqgsc1tvoe.png\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00113b6mo9vph710@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00123b6m1s13o0sp@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Lina al-Hathloul, Head of Monitoring and Advocacy at ALQST for Human Rights, questioned the assessment’s legitimacy, citing that no independent human rights organization has been able to work in Saudi Arabia, in relation to the bidding process.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00123b6m1s13o0sp@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00133b6m3vg8opky@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Al-Hathloul has experienced first-hand how brutal life in Saudi Arabia can be under MBS’ rule. Her sister was jailed in 2018 for leading a women’s rights group and remains under a travel ban, unable to leave the country. It’s been seven years since al-Hathloul, who has left the country, has seen her family, she says.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00133b6m3vg8opky@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00143b6m79a4d284@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“Saudi Arabia is a pure police state, ruled by Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman with no checks and balances,” she told&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/sport\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">CNN Sport</a>’s Amanda Davies.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00153b6mwbyvsbe1@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“He has arrested people for tweets, the executions have risen to an unprecedented number. This year, a record has been broken in Saudi Arabia’s history – 300 people have been&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ohchr.org/en/press-releases/2024/12/saudi-arabia-un-experts-voice-alarm-executions-foreign-nationals\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">executed</a>.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00153b6mwbyvsbe1@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00163b6mumat8ftt@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“Human rights defenders are put behind bars just because they advocate for women’s rights, we have seen an unprecedented level of torture and sexual harassment in prisons. My family is under an illegal travel ban just because they are a family of a women’s rights activist.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00173b6m6hb2hkd9@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“Every country violates human rights, no country is perfect, but I think it’s about red lines. Saudi Arabia, under MBS today, has crossed that red line.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00173b6m6hb2hkd9@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00183b6m47zgvx0i@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><b>News has reached out to Saudi Arabia for comment.</b></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00183b6m47zgvx0i@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00193b6mzxiqirjy@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">In its report, Clifford Chance says the assessment was produced in six weeks.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001a3b6mz4j1hmsg@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“As a function of this time frame, it is based on desk research and engagement with the Ministries identified,” it said, referring to Saudi’s Human Rights Commission, the Authority of the Care of Persons with Disabilities, the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Development, the Ministry of Interior and the Ministry of Sports.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001a3b6mz4j1hmsg@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001b3b6mjygm6nec@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“The assessment process did not involve engagement with external stakeholder/ rightsholders. In taking account of published commentary, we have focused on observations by respected monitoring bodies responsible for interpretation and monitoring implementation of the Instruments.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001b3b6mjygm6nec@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001c3b6mskdzw7ie@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Human rights groups have also criticized Saudi Arabia and FIFA for not ensuring positive change.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001c3b6mskdzw7ie@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001d3b6msl73itjr@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">HRW&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.hrw.org/report/2024/12/04/die-first-and-ill-pay-you-later/saudi-arabias-giga-projects-built-widespread\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">urged</a>&nbsp;FIFA to postpone any announcement that the World Cup would go to Saudi Arabia “until migrant workers’ and women’s rights, press freedom, and other human rights are protected.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001d3b6msl73itjr@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001f3b6myodrrtxb@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">It also called on the governing body to press Saudi Arabia to “engage with human rights stakeholders and allow independent human rights independent monitoring within the country.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001h3b6m3fcmk92x@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Meanwhile, Amnesty International has also called on FIFA to “halt the process” of awarding Saudi the tournament “unless major human rights reforms are announced.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001h3b6m3fcmk92x@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001i3b6mtje5whrx@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">In a statement to CNN, FIFA said it is “implementing thorough bidding processes for the 2030 and 2034 editions of the FIFA World Cup, in line with previous processes for the selection of hosts for the FIFA Women’s World Cup 2023 in Australia and New Zealand, the FIFA World Cup 2026 in the United States, Mexico and Canada and the FIFA Women’s World Cup 2027 in Brazil.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001i3b6mtje5whrx@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001j3b6mwfj1qo0a@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Saudi Arabia has received plenty of criticism for its human rights record before and has previously resisted allegations of “sportswashing,” which involves countries using high-profile sporting events to project a favorable image of their nation worldwide, often to shift attention away from alleged wrongdoing.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001j3b6mwfj1qo0a@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001k3b6mngywhkcj@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">In an interview with Fox News that aired in 2023, MBS said he doesn’t “care” about the country’s investments being described as sportswashing, as long as it’s “going to increase my GDP by one percent.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001k3b6mngywhkcj@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001l3b6m8rwngej8@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Earlier this year, though, the head of Saudi Arabia’s 2034 World Cup bid, Hammad Albalawi, said the country had made strides in terms of human rights in recent years.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001m3b6mw8he92bg@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“We have come a long way and there’s still a long way to go. Our principle is to develop something that is right for us. Our journey started in 2016, not because of the World Cup bid,” Albalawi&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/saudi-arabias-2034-world-cup-bid-chief-highlights-human-rights-progress-2024-12-03\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">told Reuters</a>.</p><h2 class=\"subheader inline-placeholder\" data-editable=\"text\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/subheader/instances/cm4ir36to002b3b6myz37sjwa@published\" data-component-name=\"subheader\" id=\"following-qatar\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; clear: inherit; padding: 16px 0px 8px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: var(--theme-subheader-h2__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-subheader-h2__line-height); max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><b>Following Qatar</b></h2><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001p3b6m06siwstr@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">For many soccer fans around the world, such conversations will feel familiar from previous World Cups in both Russia and Qatar, with both posing issues around human rights.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001q3b6myit7kfqc@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">The closest parallel, perhaps, is with the 2022 World Cup in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cnn.com/2022/11/17/football/qatar-2022-world-cup-migrant-workers-human-rights-spt-intl/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Qatar</a>, a nation which also received heavy criticism for its treatment of migrant workers.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001q3b6myit7kfqc@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001r3b6mz8ndaowr@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Qatar hit back at claims of sportswashing and said it would use the spotlight of the World Cup to help push the country forward.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001r3b6mz8ndaowr@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001s3b6mmfww02pa@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">In 2023, FIFA told CNN it was “undeniable that significant progress has taken place” in the country, and that the tournament was the “catalyst for these reforms.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001t3b6m9efq4gb3@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">However, Steve Cockburn, Amnesty International’s Head of Labor Rights and Sport, says that FIFA learned the wrong lessons from two years ago.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001u3b6mfz0kqutv@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“My fear is that the lesson they’ve learned from Qatar is that they can ride out the criticism. They can ride it out and prioritize the bigger political and financial goals that they’ve got,” he told CNN’s Davies.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001u3b6mfz0kqutv@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001v3b6m3zipmpm4@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Cockburn added that a tournament such as the World Cup could hold the power to bring about positive change, but only if the intentions are genuinely there to do so.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00113b6mo9vph710@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00113b6mo9vph710@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(