\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">He, like many others, was pleased that FIFA became the first global sport’s body to include human rights in such a bidding process in 2017 but has been disappointed by how it’s been implemented.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001w3b6midm0uibu@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001x3b6mj9qecq20@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“When (FIFA) is awarding what is the world’s biggest sporting event – the most watched, the most visited – it has a responsibility to make sure it’s not causing adverse impacts to workers, to fans, to activists and to journalists,” he said.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001x3b6mj9qecq20@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001y3b6mw8hbet7e@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“(FIFA) said that itself, it simply needs to live up to its own commitments and values. It’s not adhering to those standings while it’s pretending that it is. That’s a really harmful façade. We’ve had a predetermined process here.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001y3b6mw8hbet7e@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk001z3b6mcuzi73xr@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">He adds: “When it’s a choice between a World Cup in Saudi Arabia, or its human rights policies, it’s chosen a World Cup in Saudi Arabia.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00203b6mh3ftjd9p@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">Al-Hathloul, meanwhile, remains optimistic that things can still change in Saudi Arabia, saying the country’s people deserve to enjoy a World Cup, while conceding that the opportunity has been tarnished by the process.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00203b6mh3ftjd9p@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00213b6mbxvwx80j@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">She says FIFA has been “complicit” in engineering a situation whereby Saudi has faced little competition, and therefore had no incentive, to actually improve human rights.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00223b6mqzfobncn@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“In order for change to exist, you have to challenge, you have to question, you have to speak about what is going on in the country,” she said.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00223b6mqzfobncn@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00233b6m582t5po3@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“We have 10 years now, we have 10 years to encourage people to speak, we have 10 years to really challenge and question and push for positive change.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00243b6mza1wjnf6@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.292px;\">“Usually, what happens is that people have accepted Saudi money in exchange for their silence. I do hope in the coming 10 years that things will change, but people have to be braver than this.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4ir24wk00113b6mo9vph710@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inher