.87px;\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mni98j001m2cqk053ohbed@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\"><a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2024/12/12/sport/manchester-city-sinks-crisis-champions-league-spt/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Manchester City</a>&nbsp;defender Kyle Walker condemned the “vile, racist and threatening” online abuse he received on social media after the team’s 2-0 loss to Juventus in the Champions League on Wednesday.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mni98j001m2cqk053ohbed@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnmrwi0008356mcec6lwfg@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\">Walker, 34, posted two&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kylewalker2/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Instagram</a>&nbsp;Stories showing screenshots of messages he received on Thursday, one of which included a racial slur and another doctored image of him which he called “unacceptable.” The image showed what appeared to be Walker wearing a suicide bomber vest.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnmrwi0008356mcec6lwfg@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnmrwj0009356me1ci8lqo@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\">“No one should ever be subjected to the sort of vile, racist and threatening abuse I have received online since last night’s match,” Walker&nbsp;<a href=\"https://x.com/kylewalker2/status/1867223239526621434\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">wrote on Instagram and X</a>, formerly known as Twitter. “Instagram and the authorities need to stop this happening, for the sake of all who are suffering this abuse. It is never acceptable.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnmrwj000a356m1irgt92p@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\">“To our fans, we will continue to work as a team to do better, to improve and to turn the corner together.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnmrwj000b356mg08ow0mk@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\">When contacted by CNN, a spokesperson for Meta – the owner of Facebook and Instagram – said the company is working with Walker to take “appropriate action.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnmrwj000b356mg08ow0mk@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnsmh30001356mewls4oy2@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\">“No one should be subjected to racist abuse, and sending messages like this is against our rules,” the statement said. “DMs are a private messaging service, which means we can’t review or take action on a message unless the person who received the abusive DM reports it to us in-app.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4muduzr0002356mnmotgxyk@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\">“We are in touch with Kyle Walker and his team who have now reported this content and we will be taking appropriate action. No one thing will stop this behaviour overnight, but we’ll work to help protect our community from abuse, and support police investigations.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4muduzr0002356mnmotgxyk@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\"><br></p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnmrwj000c356m65thclgg@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\">Manchester City said it “strongly condemns the racist abuse” directed towards Walker.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnmrwj000d356mabn2l61o@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-size: medium; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); margin-top: var(--base-space-none); margin-left: var(--base-space-none); margin-right: var(--base-space-none); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: 118.3px;\">“We refuse to tolerate discrimination of any kind, regardless of whether that be in stadiums or online,” the club&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mancity.com/news/mens/manchester-city-club-statement-kyle-walker-63869611?utm_source=x&amp;utm_medium=organic_social\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">said</a>. “We will be offering Kyle our full support following the disgusting treatment he has received.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4mnmrwj000d356mabn2l61o@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-siz